🔥 3-Day Next.js Learning Plan

✅ Day 1: Understanding Next.js Basics
🔹 Install and set up a Next.js project
🔹 Understand Pages & Routing (App Router vs Pages Router)
🔹 Learn how getServerSideProps (SSR) & getStaticProps (SSG) work
🔹 Practice simple SSR & SSG data fetching

👨‍💻 Hands-on Exercise:

Create a home page (/)
Add an about page (/about)
Create a blog list page (/blog) using getStaticProps
✅ Day 2: API Handling & Dynamic Routing
🔹 Understand Dynamic Routes (pages/[id].js)
🔹 Learn API Routes (pages/api/) to create backend endpoints
🔹 Fetch data using Axios & fetch
🔹 Practice Client-Side Fetching (useEffect)

👨‍💻 Hands-on Exercise:

Create a blog detail page (/blog/[id]) using getStaticPaths
Build a custom API (pages/api/posts.js)
Fetch API data inside a page
✅ Day 3: Authentication & Deployment
🔹 Implement Authentication (NextAuth.js or JWT)
🔹 Learn Middleware for route protection
🔹 Deploy a Next.js app (Vercel, Netlify, or DigitalOcean)

👨‍💻 Hands-on Exercise:

Protect a page (/dashboard) so only logged-in users can access it
Deploy your project to Vercel